#          foundational dependency of fastly/pushpin (THIS) +
#          CleverCloud/clever-kubernetes-operator +
#          swir-rs/swir + diptools/dip + leon0399/ember +
#          Ragnaroek/mithril (Pure Rust Monero Miner) + 1500+
#          Rust applications needing layered configuration.
